headline: 360 Stocks in the S&P 500 Underperformed the Benchmark's 2024 Gain of 24%. Here's 2 High-Yielding S&P 500 Stocks to Buy in 2025, According to Wall Street.
summary: It's been an interesting year for the stock market.  The Invesco S&P 500 Equal Weight ETF is only up about 12%.  According to Wall Street analysts, there are at least two high-yielding dividend stocks that have trailed the broader market in 2024 but are expected to perform well in 2025.

headline: Prediction: This $43 Billion Bet Will Help Pfizer Stock Take Off in 2025.
summary: Pfizer (NYSE: PFE) became a stock market star in early pandemic days as it brought the first coronavirus vaccine to market.  The company generated billions of dollars in revenue thanks to its coronavirus vaccine and treatment, even reaching a record of more than $100 billion in total company revenue in 2022.  On top of this, some of Pfizer's blockbuster products are losing exclusivity later this decade, and this will weigh on revenue.

headline: Corporate America Drew Back From DEI. The Upheaval Isn’t Over.
summary: From Ford to Walmart, some big companies dialed back diversity efforts as activists pressed. Under the next Trump administration, the pressure will grow.
